Articles.Content: So I have been trying to get the PPD-12 Copula Module for a while now in Interstellar, but I just can't find it. I have looked through all of the tech nodes. Does anyone know where it is?[h=1][/h]
Are you using the old Interstellar or Interstellar Extended?
I am using the old version of interstellar from the original page. That might be the reason.
Thank God! Thank you so much for that question! It totally fixed everything! I was apparently missing tons of parts. Once again thank you!
